WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.800 --> 00:00:05.378
In this video, I'm going to show you my morning routine.

00:00:05.980 --> 00:00:09.240
I have a busy schedule today, so let's get started!

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:17.800
As soon as the sun starts to rise and the birds start chirping, I open my eyes. 

00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:23.460
I let the sun shine on my face and I start to think about the first thing to do today.

00:00:23.460 --> 00:00:24.840
And that's... 

00:00:24.840 --> 00:00:26.153
to continue sleeping

00:00:31.240 --> 00:00:34.440
Now that I've been able to sleep for two extra hours

00:00:34.440 --> 00:00:38.660
I notice that the sun is brighter and the birds started singing louder. 

00:00:40.400 --> 00:00:44.460
If I turn around right now, maybe I can sleep just a little more. 

00:00:52.280 --> 00:00:55.960
Now that it's later in the morning, I think the sun is calling me!

00:00:56.720 --> 00:01:00.060
"Djamila, wake up" 

00:01:01.160 --> 00:01:04.440
Now, it really is time to start listening to nature. 

00:01:05.460 --> 00:01:08.040
I push the covers aside, I get up

00:01:08.460 --> 00:01:10.900
and the first thing I do is.. 

00:01:11.340 --> 00:01:13.340
close the curtains.

00:01:15.180 --> 00:01:17.860
And then, I crawl back into my warm bed.

00:01:22.820 --> 00:01:27.160
Okay, so now I'm well rested, the only thing that's left to do is stretch

00:01:27.160 --> 00:01:29.480
and then I really do need to get up. 

00:01:30.060 --> 00:01:35.960
I push the covers away, I get out of bed and I put on my super comfy slippers. 

00:01:36.960 --> 00:01:38.960
Then, I walk to the bathroom

00:01:38.960 --> 00:01:40.780
I high-five Hyder

00:01:41.340 --> 00:01:43.311
I wash my face

00:01:44.700 --> 00:01:51.020
I put on some lotion, and then I notice that I'm starting to crave a Nutella sandwich. 

00:01:51.720 --> 00:01:54.700
So, I walk to the kitchen and grab all the necessities. 

00:02:05.640 --> 00:02:06.420
Oh no!

00:02:07.380 --> 00:02:08.860
The jar is empty!

00:02:12.020 --> 00:02:15.560
Noooooooooooooo

00:02:22.960 --> 00:02:24.580
Thank goodness... 

00:02:25.080 --> 00:02:26.801
it was only a dream.

00:02:31.380 --> 00:02:33.380
Good night :) 

